{"tid":1474220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油麻地劏房揭命案　23歲男手腳被綁膠袋笠頭　警調查指無可疑","createTime":"2019-08-15T05:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:30:20.000Z","uid":53379,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d113f66d2b9e7df9017abdb0308d61380db1c9","tid":1474220,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">油麻地劏房揭命案　23歲男手腳被綁膠袋笠頭　警調查指無可疑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日傍晚6時18 分，警方接獲一名非華裔男子報案，指油麻地上海街113號一個低層劏房單位傳出異味，鄰居報警後，警方及消防登門，爆門入屋後發現一具南亞裔男子屍體倒卧單位內，男死者23歲。警方其後封鎖現場，正調查死亡原因，案件改列屍體發現案處理，由油尖重案組接手。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方入屋後發現死者頭笠膠袋，一隻手被毛巾綁住，雙腳被膠紙綁起，大字型綁在一張碌架床上。</span>然而經警方調查後，認為事件無可疑，死者死因有待驗屍確定。至今早（15日）肇事單位已解封，有鄰居指男事主居於上址約4至5個月，近期不見他出入單位，至昨日單位傳出臭味。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/363941/%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%8F%AD%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E8%86%A0%E8%A2%8B%E7%AC%A0%E9%A0%AD-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91?fbclid=IwAR2MINeri4MSuwuSb1rPI0qNYaoXRt226X_W4MjKSrCaXqRqpdFfXrzJI60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F363941%2F%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588-23%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25B6%2581%25E8%2586%25A0%25E8%25A2%258B%25E7%25AC%25A0%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2596%2591%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2MINeri4MSuwuSb1rPI0qNYaoXRt226X_W4MjKSrCaXqRqpdFfXrzJI60&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=98f52f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/363941/%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%8F%AD%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E8